This page generates a new Leviar wallet. It is self contained and does all the necessary calculations locally, so is suitable for generating a new wallet on a machine that is not connected to the network, and may even never be. This way, you can create a Leviar Wallet without risking the keys.
You can check for up to date versions of this tool here.

  • Wallet Generator

Custom entropy for deterministic wallet
(leave empty to use the browser's PRNG)

WARNING: entropy is way too low for the wallet to be secure: aim for 256 bits (about a hundred dice throws)

Public address

This is the address you give to third parties to send Leviar to you. It is the only information here that's meant to be public.

Mnemonic seed

The mnemonic seed is a string that comprises 25 words and allows you to recreate your private keys. Keep it secure!

weekday height recipe aimless enmity fossil tomorrow dented framed dexterity fountain because linen sailor racetrack queen yawning railway paper eccentric olive dime awful bamboo dexterity

Private keys (optional)

The spend key and view key are the raw private keys for the new wallet. They are here for your information, since they can be recovered using the mnemonic seed in the above box. If you decide to keep them, keep them secure.
